Detailed Descriptions of Key Components
content_recommender.py
Purpose: Central to the AI-driven content recommendation system. Analyzes user interactions to suggest personalized content, enhancing user engagement.
Functionality:
Data Loading: Integrates user data for model input.
Model Training: Utilizes algorithms like KNN or matrix factorization.
Evaluation: Measures accuracy with metrics like RMSE.
Prediction: Delivers personalized content suggestions.
Model Persistence: Saves and reloads models for efficiency.
chatbot_service.py
Purpose: Manages the chatbot for interactive user support across the platform.
Functionality:
Initialization: Sets up the chatbot with necessary configurations.
Training: Feeds conversational data for effective response generation.
Response Generation: Crafts and delivers responses based on user queries.
Logging and Error Handling: Monitors interactions and manages errors.
Persistence: Maintains chatbot state across sessions.
vr_experiences.py
Purpose: Bridges VR technology with blog content to provide immersive and interactive user experiences.
Functionality:
Scene Management: Loads and initializes VR scenes from configurations.
Content Synchronization: Links VR scenes with relevant blog posts.
User Interaction: Manages input methods and collects user feedback.
Performance Optimization: Ensures smooth performance and accessibility.
Configuration Management: Handles storage and versioning of VR settings.